# 🐱 Cat Login — Playful and Interactive Login Form

A fun and interactive login page featuring a cute orange cat 🧡 that reacts to user actions.  
Designed to make logging in a little more playful, friendly, and full of good vibes 😺  

---

## 🌐 Live Demo  
[👉 View it here!](https://yuozarseiph.github.io/cat-login/)

---

## ✨ Features  
- 🐾 Clean, modern and minimal UI  
- ✉️ Email and password input fields  
- 👁️ Show / Hide password toggle  
- 💾 Remember-me checkbox  
- 📱 Fully responsive layout  
- 🌈 Gradient background and soft shadows  

---

## 🚀 How to Run  

This is a static project — no frameworks or build steps needed!  

### Option 1 — Using Python 3 (Windows PowerShell)
```pwsh
Set-Location -Path 'D:\React Projects\Programming Files\login-cat'
py -m http.server 8000

Then open your browser and go to 👉 http://localhost:8000

